{"tid":164047,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「科學」大家信唔信陰陽眼？","createTime":"2017-03-20T11:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T03:58:06.000Z","uid":21161,"like":33,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83cfde831684ca33d9c7f34cc1d260a5ac6eb2c2","tid":164047,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"相傳有陰影眼既人會睇到鬼魂<br />\n例如有人跳樓自殺之後 <br />\n佢個靈魂會不斷重覆呢個動作<br />\n而有陰陽眼既人就係見到佢<br />\n甚至可以溝通 証明個隻鬼既身份等等<br />\n<br />\n而科學家既角度就係認為係來自精神分裂症造成既幻覺或妄想<br />\n但係問題就黎啦<br />\n有兩個都擁有陰陽眼既人 <br />\n佢地都睇到同一個既鬼魂既存在<br />\n咁姐係証明左佢見到既野係同一樣野？真係存在？<br />\n定係集體幻覺？<br />\n<br />\n其實信科學既人都唔會信陰陽眼<br />\n因為信陰陽眼既話姐係變相信鬼神既存在<br />\n<br />\n大家信唔信呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔信"},{"pid":"de562a090e43031de2c310d4377b8a10ae20f5b8","tid":164047,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfd093a6d1bcd7d535733d77410c080fc67fe56","tid":164047,"uid":47797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"我無但信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad84222c66e7febfde73024969bc229dc651056","tid":164047,"uid":21161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我無但信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你會信既？<br />\n信陰陽眼 其實姐係變相認同鬼既存在喎<br />\n連登仔可能會challenge你 又相鬼神又剩 但又反耶撚"},{"pid":"0ecf878b14749b284c4d5fa785ab5498a6b0d131","tid":164047,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我無但信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你會信既？<br />\n信陰陽眼 其實姐係變相認同鬼既存在喎<br />\n連登仔可能會challenge你 又相鬼神又剩 但又反耶撚</blo